data.value:
Billy was found by the roadside back in March 2016. We do not understand why she has not been adopted; she really is a special cat.
Billy is very laid back. She likes nothing bettter than a knee to unwind on her two favourite past time are eating (a lot) and sleeping!
Billy is the most loving and cuddling cat you would wish for. She is extremely patient with children and has never shown any signs of aggression at all. She is fine with other cats, but prefers humans!" Billy is a healthy cat, good with dogs or cats or kids. Her only fault is she is rather food of sofas so best to keep her nails neatly trimmed.
